name: Welcome Michael Jackson!!!
description:
Welcome Michael !! We are very happy that you have signed to participate a season in "Fuck the dollar, give me your tezos", just stay away from my wife and my children, I hope that with the proceeds we can buy you a latex nose.
(THIS DRAWING DOES NOT BELONG TO THE COLLECTION, IT IS ONLY YOUR LETTER OF PRESENTATION). If you have this drawing and the one of "Tomy, the human centipede", fuck the dollar part 5 is FREE for you. Collect all your cards for future benefits.
